ransportet tilbake til sin b\u00e5s p\u00e5 Leangen Travbane.", "- Det vil opprettes straffesak mot kusken for brudd p\u00e5 veitrafikklovens paragraf 21 p\u00e5 f\u00f8ring av et kj\u00f8ret\u00f8y i beruset tilstand, opplyser Brevik."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|trondheim"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "4307945ef2e9ed35082e1e82149ac71391f9154b6bd886f71ca8c0f07e6995a4"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2014-12-13T19:14:18.656Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Kj\u00f8rte i hest og vogn over Blomsterbua."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article9936347.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/kusuk12333.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/657b50d01baabd3d3ffd47f3e25ab265c1685798.jpg?589cc121"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Politiet p\u00e5grep beruset kusk -adressa.no", "Bl\u00e5ste over to i promille", "Skulle p\u00e5 bar"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "657b50d01baabd3d3ffd47f3e25ab265c1685798"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["politiet", "kusk", "politiet p\u00e5grep beruset", "beruset tilstand", "beruset", "vogn", "p\u00e5grep beruset kusk", "hest"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["blomsterbrua", "twitter", "nordre gate og fjordgata", "midtbyen", "fjordgata", "nordre gate", "leangen travbane", "blomsterbua"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["s\u00f8r-tr\u00f8ndelag", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["frank brevik", "olav skarsem"]}, {"fiel